para_trans: The posts of Chief Engineer, Water Resources Department, Konkan Region, Mumbai, Superintending Engineer, South Konkan Irrigation Project Board, Sindhudurg City Board, Executive Engineer, Sindhudurg Irrigation Project Construction Department, Charathe Sawantwadi Division, Tillari Main Dam Sub-division, Tillarinagar Sub-division are vacant. 01.09.2025 that is. Regarding the extension to 28.02.2026.
Government Decision No. Issue 2025 / Q. No.39 / Javi
Madam Kama Marg, Martyr Rajguru Chowk,
Reference: 1) Government Decision No: Issue 2025 / Q. No.31 / JV, D. 08.04.2025 2) Letter from the Chief Engineer, Water Resources Department, Konkan Region, Mumbai
3) Department of Finance, Government Decision No. Posts-2016 / P.S.No.8 / 16 / APC,

Chief Engineer, Water Resources Department, Konkan Region, Mumbai, Superintending Engineer, South Konkan Irrigation Project Board, Sindhudurg City Board, Executive Engineer, Sindhudurg Irrigation Project Construction Department, Charathe Sawantwadi Division, Tillari Main Dam subdivision, Tillarinagar subdivision, 18 posts on fixed temporary establishment and 01 post on converted temporary establishment. 01.09.2025 that is. The government is approving an extension until 28.02.2026. (Details are provided in the accompanying form.) )

The cost of the establishment to be registered under this designation shall be incurred under the head "I-3, Account Title 2801 Seeds, 01 Hydropower Generation, 001 Operations and Administration, (05) Tillari Hydropower Project, (05) (01) Superintending Engineer, South Konkan Irrigation Board, Oros, Sindhudurg (Compulsory) (2801 2203)" and shall be met from the grant sanctioned thereunder.

3. The said Government Decision Government Decision No. The posts are being issued in accordance with the powers conferred on the Administrative Department vide Notification No.8 / 16 / APC, dated 26.08.2025.
The Government decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
